data.description: ***$5,000 Painting and Flooring Allowance*** Charming and spacious 3-bedroom home, with a comfortable and inviting living space for those seeking a cozy and well-maintained home. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the open split floor plan, which creates a seamless flow throughout the house. The primary suite features a walk-in closet, double vanity, walk-in shower, and jetted tub. Good sized rooms and closets, foyer with a coat closet, plus a huge backyard! ***No Owner Financing*****No Assumable Loan*** First Horizon Bank "Eveonne Lindsey" is offering qualified buyer/s an $8,000 grant towards the purchase of this home. Any legitimate mortgage or bank pre-approval letter will be accepted for this purchase.
